      <title>韩国对华投资流量创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/south-korea-direct-investment-flow-to-china-falls-most-on-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，韩国对中国的直接投资流量出现三十多年前的最大降幅，这表明随着美国敦促其盟友减少对北京的依赖，两国之间的经济关系正在减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/south-korea-direct-investment-flow-to-china-falls-most-on-record</guid>
